        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Ashley chooses <strong>one (1) willing creature</strong> within <strong>5 feet</strong> of her who can see or hear her. The target can’t be benefiting from any effect that grants an additional Action this round (such as haste, Action Surge, or another Dance). The target can <strong>immediately use its reaction</strong> to, in any order,</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>- <strong>move up to its speed</strong> (this movement is normal movement), and</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>- <strong>take either one extra Action or Bonus Action</strong>, which, if this is an Action, can be used only to take the Attack (one weapon attack only), Dash, Disengage, Hide, or Use an Object Action.</p></li></ul></div></div>",
